&CONTROL
   calculation      = 'relax',
   prefix           = 'oxygen_sys',
   outdir           = './out',
   pseudo_dir       = '/yourdir/PSPOT',
   tstress          = .true.,
   tprnfor          = .true.,
/

&SYSTEM
   ibrav            = 0,
   nat              = 2,
   ntyp             = 1,
   ecutwfc          = 60,
   ecutrho          = 500,
   occupations      = 'smearing',
   smearing         = 'mp',
   degauss          = 0.01,
   nspin            = 2,
   starting_magnetization(1) = 0.8,
   starting_magnetization(2) = 0.8,
/

&ELECTRONS
   conv_thr         = 1.0d-8,
/

&IONS
/

CELL_PARAMETERS angstrom
7.0 0.0 0.0
0.0 7.5 0.0
0.0 0.0 8.0

ATOMIC_SPECIES
O 15.999 o_pbe_v1.2.uspp.F.UPF

ATOMIC_POSITIONS angstrom
O  0.0 0.0 0.0        
O  0.0 0.0 1.21
  
K_POINTS automatic
1 1 1 0 0 0
